0Z","msg":"冇錯呀，所以當資料愈多愈可以反映到個人適唔適應到果個國家，又可以睇埋佢追求既生活會有咩唔好既地方，佢肯唔肯取捨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcef41d2ce3b57b3511849b0f95468b15c35533","tid":2311681,"uid":20405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad4c1a97d2c2c57773d77f88e599071806c7594e","tid":2311681,"uid":221650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:19:11.000Z","msg":"根據現時難度<br />\n加&gt;英&gt;澳&gt;美"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"方法有好多種既，唔一定投資<br />\n<br />\n英國有BNO就已易好多"},{"pid":"c30068e156cfd30f0f515a8eab4d7dde7844cf8c","tid":2311681,"uid":221650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fcef41d2ce3b57b3511849b0f95468b15c35533","tid":2311681,"uid":20405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad4c1a97d2c2c57773d77f88e599071806c7594e","tid":2311681,"uid":221650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:19:11.000Z","msg":"根據現時難度<br />\n加&gt;英&gt;澳&gt;美"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"方法有好多種既，唔一定投資<br />\n<br />\n英國有BNO就已易好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"就係計埋現時既方便之門<br />\n<br />\n加拿大係最易，唔洗 BNO，唔洗當地讀書，到埗後要 1-3 年時間就有 PR<br />\n<br />\n&gt;<br />\n<br />\n英國，要 BNO，唔洗讀書，5 年時間<br />\n<br />\n&gt;<br />\n<br />\n澳洲，唔洗 BNO，<span class=\"red\">要當地讀書</span>，花最少 5 年<br />\n<br />\n&gt;<br />\n<br />\n美國，無針對性 safe haven 計劃，只有將香港列入難民地區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳洲當地讀書一般花你 6-80 萬學費生活，先有資格申請 TR，再要 5 年先 PR，難度顯然更高"},{"pid":"3614b74fff45b4f08fe6eb9fdb58bf98934324cf","tid":2311681,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e588ed0c206286bbd1dfe87ae965bc5af41d29dc","tid":2311681,"uid":20405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4f534089f0e62daed62e804e70498b425ea96e3","tid":2311681,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:15:27.000Z","msg":"移去西伯利亞隱居<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-0